{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3295a812db","title":"对王鹤寿关于企业思想政治工作报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9f8552bb5c","index":0,"year":1963,"month":12,"day":11,"articleId":"3295a812db"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f8fc4d703a","type":"title","text":"对王鹤寿关于企业思想政治工作报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3295a812db"},{"id":"e7572bb1e7","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3295a812db"},{"id":"5328fd7925","type":"appellation","text":"薄一波同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3295a812db"},{"id":"e42b61fc86","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请你看一下。别的工业部是否也抓起了思想政治工作，请你查告我。看来学解放军，并且调一些解放军好干部到工业部门工作，是一个好办法。请你考虑一下这个问题。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3295a812db"},{"id":"0f5de28ece","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十二月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3295a812db"}],"page":{"id":"f9045045ab","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3295a812db","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"6c38d5f129","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"3295a812db","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王鹤寿，当时任冶金工业部部长、中共冶金工业部党组书记。"},{"id":"9ab34a83c5","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"3295a812db","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指王鹤寿1963年12月9日关于企业思想政治工作问题给毛泽东的报告。报告说，今年我们在企业里，除了进行社会主义教育和开展增产节约、“五反”运动以外，主要抓了两件事：一是开展“经济活动分析”，一是学习解放军的政治工作。经济活动分析是在一个企业或班组里，拿它这一个月的各种经济指标（产量、质量、成本、品种、消耗、回收率、劳动生产率等）与上月比，与最好的季度比，与别的企业、班组比，与世界先进水平比，从这种比较中找出差距以及产生差距的原因。学习解放军的政治工作，就是用解放军的政治工作的方法，发扬主席过去所批示的《鞍钢宪法》精神。这不仅使我们找到了做好企业思想政治工作的范例，而且解决了许多过去长期没有解决的问题，效果是显著的。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2de1c65b21","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"3295a812db"},{"id":"4411eb29bf","type":"title","text":"对王鹤寿“关于企业思想政治工作报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"3295a812db"},{"id":"6c38d5f129","type":"paragraph","text":"薄一波同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"3295a812db"},{"id":"865b1bcfd9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"3295a812db"},{"id":"9ab34a83c5","type":"paragraph","text":"此件回请你看一下。别的工业部是否也抓起了思想政治工作，请你查告我。看来学解放军，并且调一些解放军好干部到工业部门工作，是一个好办法。请你考虑一下这个问题","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"3295a812db"}],"page":{"id":"f34594f5df","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"3295a812db","start":138,"end":138}}}},"__N_SSG":true}